# FactFlip

**Multiplication Facts Practice • Skip Counting Visuals • Instant Feedback**

A web app that helps kids truly *understand* multiplication facts using visual skip-counting and the commutative property.

Built as a single HTML file.

- **Practice Mode**  
  - Skip-counting with glowing dots  
  - **FLIP** button instantly swaps factors (teaches commutativity)  
  - Final answer appears when complete  

- **Test Mode**  
  - 4 smart multiple-choice answers (two other multiples + one off-by-one)  
  - Instant green/red feedback + correct answer reveal  

- **Smart Fact Selection**  
  - Toggle any individual fact from 2×2 to 9×9  
  - “Select All / Clear All” buttons  
  - Never repeats the same fact immediately  

---

## Tech Stack

- Pure HTML5 + Tailwind CSS + Vanilla JavaScript
- Zero dependencies
- Single file (≈ 12 KB)

---

Prototype built with SuperGrok 4.20
